'''Religious socialism''' is any form of [[socialism]] based on [[religious values]]. Members of several major [[religion]]s have found that their beliefs about [[human society]] fit with socialist principles and ideas. As a result, religious socialist movements have developed within these religions. Such movements include:
* [[Buddhist socialism]]
* [[Christian socialism]]
* [[Islamic socialism]]
* [[Jewish left|Jewish socialism]]

